Package com.ibm.as400.access.jdbcClient

Class Main

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.as400.access.jdbcClient.Main
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable
public class Main extends Object implements Runnable
Main class for the jdbcClient program. This sample client uses JDBC to connect to the specified URL using the specified userid and password.

This program is provided AS/IS and formal support will NOT be provided. This program should not be used in a production environment.

Because this program is provided AS/IS, no consideration is made for NLS support.
